# Playwright Integration

Used by: QAAgent

## Purpose
Run automated browser tests generated by QAAgent.

## Actions Available
- Run test suite
- Generate test report
- Screenshot on failure
- Record test execution

## When It Triggers
- After QAAgent output is approved: automatically run generated tests
- On SelfHealingAgent retry: re-run failed tests

## Configuration
- Test output directory: defined in environment variables
- Browser: chromium (default)
- Headless: true (default)